Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.03,0:00:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你...你怎么了？香草\N有什么地方不舒服吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.97,0:00:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你没事吧，请振作一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.04,0:00:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟糕，再这样下去\N香草会死掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.21,0:00:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦，怎...怎么办才好...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.28,0:00:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请原谅愚蠢的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.35,0:00:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我所犯下的罪过\N我会亲自偿还
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.69,0:00:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请原谅我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.29,0:00:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，香草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.50,0:00:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,银河天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.84,0:00:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么？为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.04,0:00:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危机，这下糟糕了\N紧张！紧张！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.85,0:00:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻烦光线  BURU  BURU
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.78,0:00:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙大骚动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.95,0:00:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OK，胡闹一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.82,0:01:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也没关系，吃个饮茶\N好啊！好啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.63,0:01:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱着欢悦的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.79,0:01:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最后一起向神明祈祷吧\NBANG  BANG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.00,0:01:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因果报应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.53,0:01:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每天都是冒险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.30,0:01:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一旦开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.27,0:01:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就让它顺其自然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.71,0:01:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有机关，没有魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.15,0:01:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孤注一掷的I.N.G.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.48,0:01:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无忧无虑的狂欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.95,0:01:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梦想与希望的机关枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.82,0:01:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,锁定想要的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.16,0:01:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,BANG  BANG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.16,0:01:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跳舞吧，玩吧\NBRAVO！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.86,0:01:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐上令人兴奋的火箭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.47,0:01:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开辟天下无敌的成功之路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.01,0:02:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(遗失物品菜肉浓汤)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.82,0:02:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.19,0:02:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么要开枪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.26,0:02:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀，因为吓了一跳\N不小心就开枪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.16,0:02:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么会有这种人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.33,0:02:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优，你刚才说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.13,0:02:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个...那个...\N香草再这样下去会死掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.23,0:02:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我问你为什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.73,0:02:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她已经两个礼拜没吃东西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.50,0:02:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.24,0:02:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.24,0:02:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为忏悔而断食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.21,0:02:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,断食？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.64,0:02:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是两星期前发生的事\N我和香草一起在街上巡逻时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.45,0:02:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草好像把什么\N重要的东西给弄丢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.89,0:02:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是什么东西呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.99,0:02:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是那个很重要的东西呀\N香草总是随身带着走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.57,0:02:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有那种东西吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.50,0:02:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你连这个也不知道吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.84,0:02:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草经常把那个东西\N紧握在手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.64,0:03:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那时也是，那时也是，那时也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.84,0:03:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我问那是什么东西啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.91,0:03:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道\N没看过也没听说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.85,0:03:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.78,0:03:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你刚才不是一副知道的口气吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.15,0:03:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只说我知道\N她紧握着什么东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.46,0:03:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我一句也没说过\N我知道那个是什么东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.63,0:03:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果把那个东西弄丢了\N在找到之前必须断食吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.30,0:03:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.46,0:03:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是这样持续断食下去\N香草她会....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.20,0:03:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以，所以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.37,0:03:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们不快点找到那个东西的话\N香草会死掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.81,0:03:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来如此\N是这样子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.78,0:03:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，实际上有点困难\N虽然我很想帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.49,0:03:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是不知道那个失物是什么\N那要怎么找呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.39,0:03:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没问题\N我们可以去拜托"银河之母"呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.53,0:03:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,银河之母？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.40,0:03:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是谁啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.47,0:04:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我来介绍...这位是银河之母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.91,0:04:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是兰花吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.58,0:04:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不对\N虽然有点像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.31,0:04:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是占卜师的"银河之母"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.08,0:04:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，兰花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.65,0:04:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,银河之母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.09,0:04:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.49,0:04:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.32,0:04:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫她兰花没回应\N叫她银河之母就有回应了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.16,0:04:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这证明了她不是兰花喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.03,0:04:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么证据啊\N喂，兰花，你给我醒来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.06,0:04:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.10,0:04:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在西北方位\N好像坐着一位有困扰的年轻人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.00,0:04:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那里有鲸鱼居住的海洋\N想找的东西就在那附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.01,0:04:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一点也听不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.64,0:04:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,西北...西北方...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.05,0:04:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有鲸鱼喷水池\N烦恼的年轻人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.35,0:04:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沉思者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.08,0:04:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捕鲸街A地区\N那边也是巡逻的区域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.62,0:04:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有可能是那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.76,0:05:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果兰花的占卜可信的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.87,0:05:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄荷，谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.73,0:05:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我接受这个寻找失物的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.80,0:05:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,命名为"寻找失物小队"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.74,0:05:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,LET'S  GO
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.15,0:05:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草，等我回来喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.55,0:05:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，小狗狗，好可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.92,0:05:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，好可怕喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.06,0:05:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起\N请问鲸鱼喷水池在哪里呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.23,0:05:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪？\N我还以为是人，原来是鲸鱼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.60,0:05:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪？原来是这里呀\N遗失物在哪里呢...啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.07,0:05:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.81,0:05:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草，是这个吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.11,0:05:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.64,0:05:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彩券？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.28,0:05:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.22,0:06:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中奖了\N第一特奖5000万
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.69,0:06:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.82,0:06:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优真厉害\N香草的失物一定是这个东西啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.19,0:06:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优的运气还是一样好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.96,0:06:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能够提前解决，实在太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.77,0:06:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.94,0:06:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.77,0:06:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在搞什么啊\N怎么把5000万给丢了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.01,0:06:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？香草怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.58,0:06:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.25,0:06:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗？\N找错东西就没有意义了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.59,0:06:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么嘛，我真是的\N找错东西了还这么高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.52,0:06:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行啊，我真笨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.49,0:06:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我再去找一遍，银河之母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.60,0:06:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，对喔，占卜是吗？\N好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.77,0:06:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.70,0:06:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在物欲混沌的河流当中\N螃蟹在蠕动着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.34,0:06:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概是指繁华街吧\N在五号街有家螃蟹专卖店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.31,0:06:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那附近的箱子里\N有个闪闪发光的物体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.81,0:07:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交给我吧，我这就出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.32,0:07:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这次一定要找到...\N啊，坏小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.52,0:07:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.69,0:07:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可怕...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.09,0:07:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.86,0:07:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,箱子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.56,0:07:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.97,0:07:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了\N是这个吧，香草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.77,0:07:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.77,0:07:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你又捡到一个不得了的东西耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.37,0:07:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个是宇宙纪元前黄金王朝的\N多耶王三世穿戴过的27点首饰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.75,0:07:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其中的红宝石\N单单一个就要八千万呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.72,0:07:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来如此，所以才会随身携带啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.12,0:07:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草，对不起，这么久才找到\N给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.96,0:07:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.23,0:07:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在想什么啊？真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.60,0:07:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好不容易可以当上大富翁的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.04,0:07:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.41,0:08:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我又捡错东西回来了是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.18,0:08:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我再去找找\N这次一定会好好找回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.88,0:08:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我出门了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.35,0:08:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，她没听我的占卜就走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.29,0:08:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三次的出发...啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.00,0:08:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.84,0:08:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.84,0:08:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我忘了问地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.71,0:08:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以就先把那附近掉的东西\N全带回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.81,0:08:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，那个不是中国传说中的\N"天命招魂壶"吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.78,0:08:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,据说已经不存在在世界上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.25,0:08:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？值多少钱呢\N不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.89,0:08:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果收藏家知道这还存在的话\N一定价值数亿元以上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.49,0:08:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,数亿元？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.26,0:08:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.27,0:09:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我又找错了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.01,0:09:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草，这样有点过份吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.31,0:09:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄...薄荷，没关系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.28,0:09:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好，这种态度不好吧，香草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.82,0:09:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优这么努力在帮你找了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.72,0:09:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啊，就算找错了\N也不用着把它丢掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.93,0:09:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,努力找东西的梅尔优好可怜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.30,0:09:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别这样说，我没关系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.83,0:09:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不觉得这样\N梅尔优太可怜了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.40,0:09:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太过份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.34,0:09:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个...那个...\N你还是向她道歉比较好...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.44,0:09:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错，跟梅尔优道歉，香草\N那个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.25,0:09:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优，怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.99,0:09:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草没有错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.02,0:10:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们不要欺负香草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.23,0:10:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了，我知道了\N梅尔优不要哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.60,0:10:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会再骂香草了，别哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.47,0:10:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如此大的风波当中\N我拿着吸尘器吸地板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.51,0:10:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许大家会认为我是无情的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.55,0:10:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是并非如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.38,0:10:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我现在这种波涛汹涌的心情\N只能靠打扫这方法来分散注意力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.62,0:10:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起...女孩们...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.63,0:10:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯？什么东西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.87,0:10:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草她...香草她...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.97,0:10:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是因为找不到重要的东西\N而心急的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.37,0:10:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯...对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.57,0:10:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,垃圾塞住了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.21,0:10:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊...你的鼻子都是鼻涕呀\N快把鼻涕擤掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.65,0:10:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.49,0:11:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.22,0:11:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起，我已经没事了\N我再去找一遍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.86,0:11:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个到底是什么东西啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.47,0:11:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听说那是信徒\N必须持有的护身符
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.51,0:11:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了，找到就好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.15,0:11:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总之，梅尔优辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.78,0:11:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀\N梅尔优那家伙竟然睡着了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.49,0:11:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草，太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.23,0:11:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.87,0:11:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下个菜单是  “烧烤盒装少女”\N佛特是个好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.67,0:11:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很会照顾人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.94,0:11:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最喜欢吃不甜的苹果派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.07,0:11:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是个很重要的伙伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.91,0:11:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是宇宙的大英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.58,0:11:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听说要颁发名誉勋章给她喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.53,0:12:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,满天的星辰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.33,0:12:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像是打翻水瓶似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.67,0:12:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,躺在新月下的吊床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.48,0:12:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作了梦之后，变得想见你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.12,0:12:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,侧耳倾听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.29,0:12:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看，不是听见了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.19,0:12:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令人兴奋的天线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.27,0:12:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就让它睡着吧  NO  NO
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.34,0:13:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,处女座的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.28,0:13:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向牡羊座的你发出信号\N急电，急电
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.35,0:13:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乘着飞马的翅膀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.45,0:13:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前去迎接你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.59,0:13:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,DARING  LOVING  YOU

